No. 11815. Mitz et al. v. Friedman et al. Decided April 25, 1911. Error to Circuit Court-of Richland county; Mr. A. A. Douglass and Messrs. Reed & Beach,- for plaintiffs in error. Messrs. Cummings, McBride & Wolfe, for defendants in error. Davis, Price and Johnson, JJ., concur.

Judgment affirmed.
